The Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) in Bauchi state is set to collate and announce the long awaited Tafawa Balewa LGA results of the state governorship election held on March 9. Our reporter says the INEC may also formally declare the winner of the Bauchi state governorship election immediately after announcing the poll results of the pending local government today.  Details later… INEC’s inconsistency over Bauchi guber elections worrisome - Civil society Bauchi Guber Poll: APC rejects INEC decision on Tafawa Balewa Bauchi: CSO accuses INEC of inconsistent decisions